flowchart TD
    A[Client / Postman\nPOST /generate] --> B[Express API\nindex.js]

    B --> C{Validate Request}
    C -->|Missing requirement| C1[400 Bad Request]
    C -->|Valid| D[QA Agent Loop\nOpenAI tool-calling]

    subgraph RAG ["RAG Pipeline"]
        E1[search_knowledge_base]
        E2[(Vectra Vector Store\nQA Best Practices)]
        E3[OpenAI Embeddings\ntext-embedding-3-small]
        E1 --> E3 --> E2
        E2 -->|Top-K relevant docs| E1
    end

    subgraph Agent ["Autonomous Agent — Tool Execution"]
        F1[Tool: search_knowledge_base]
        F2[Tool: generate_test_cases]
        F3[Tool: validate_test_cases]
        F4[Tool: revise_test_cases\nonly if score below 8]

        F1 -->|Retrieved QA context| F2
        F2 -->|Generated test cases| F3
        F3 -->|Validation score + issues| F4
        F4 -->|Revised test cases| G[Final Output]
        F3 -->|Score >= 8| G
    end

    D --> F1
    F1 <--> E1

    subgraph Reflection ["Reflection / Self-Correction"]
        H1[reflect — score output 0-10]
        H2{Score < 8?}
        H3[revise — fix identified issues]
        H4[Accept output]
        H1 --> H2
        H2 -->|Yes| H3
        H2 -->|No| H4
    end

    G --> H1
    H3 --> I[Final Revised Output]
    H4 --> I

    I --> J{MongoDB available?}
    J -->|Yes| J1[(MongoDB\nTestCase collection)]
    J -->|No| J2[Skip persistence\nreturn response only]
    J1 --> K[200 JSON Response\noutput + agentTrace + reflection]
    J2 --> K

    subgraph Fallback ["Fallback Mode (missing/invalid key or quota exceeded)"]
        L[Local template generator]
    end

    B -->|No key / 401 / 429| L
    L --> J
